### EPUB Structure Extractor API
### Requires the REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/v1
@epubPath = /workspace/extractor/my_book.epub
@jsonOutput = /workspace/extractor/output/book_with_summaries.json
@marpOutput = /workspace/extractor/output/book_presentation.md

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Health
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Root
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Books
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### List books (paginated)
GET {{apiUrl}}/books?skip=0&limit=10

### Get book by ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/1

### Create a book
POST {{apiUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clean Architecture",
  "author": "Robert C. Martin",
  "isbn": "978-0134494166",
  "description": "A guide to software structure and design.",
  "language": "en",
  "publisher": "Prentice Hall",
  "publication_date": "2017"
}

### Delete a book
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/books/1

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Chapters
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### List chapters for a book
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/1/chapters

### Get chapter by ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/chapters/1

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Metadata
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get metadata for a book
GET {{apiUrl}}/books/1/metadata

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Processing Jobs
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all jobs
GET {{apiUrl}}/jobs

### List jobs filtered by status  (pending | processing | completed | failed)
GET {{apiUrl}}/jobs?status=pending

### Get job by ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/jobs/1

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Statistics
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Global stats
GET {{apiUrl}}/stats

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Search
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Search books
GET {{apiUrl}}/search/books?q=clean

### Search chapters (all books)
GET {{apiUrl}}/search/chapters?q=architecture

### Search chapters within a specific book
GET {{apiUrl}}/search/chapters?q=architecture&book_id=1

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# EPUB Processing
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Check LLM connectivity (Ollama)
GET {{apiUrl}}/epub/llm/status

### 2. Extract EPUB structure → JSON
POST {{apiUrl}}/epub/extract
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "epub_path": "{{epubPath}}",
  "json_output": "{{jsonOutput}}"
}

### 3. Generate AI summaries (requires Ollama — run step 2 first)
POST {{apiUrl}}/epub/summarize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "json_path": "{{jsonOutput}}"
}

### 4. Generate Marp presentation (run step 2 first)
POST {{apiUrl}}/epub/marp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "json_path": "{{jsonOutput}}",
  "marp_output": "{{marpOutput}}",
  "title": "My Book Summary",
  "include_summaries": true,
  "include_content": false,
  "max_depth": 3
}

### 5. List sections of an extracted book
GET {{apiUrl}}/epub/sections?book_key={{jsonOutput}}

### 6. Set excluded sections (run step 2 first)
POST {{apiUrl}}/epub/sections/exclude
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "book_key": "{{jsonOutput}}",
  "excluded_ids": ["1", "2.1","3","4","5","6","21","22"],
  "excluded_titles": ["Review Questions"]
}

